{"tid":365340,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[無圖]我叫唔叫中左伏？(延續）","createTime":"2017-08-19T06:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T14:35:14.000Z","uid":79981,"like":7,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d055afa2da37412a6e76bae25e52c48b097cbd07","tid":365340,"uid":79981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:58:57.000Z","msg":"延續返上一次染柒左嘅po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼之前染衰左之後一直都無搞過個頭 見個頭又金又黃咁最近唔洗點出街 就心血來潮咁買兩包試下個效果 衰左都可以帶帽嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/145717_4d5b00cb8685042b20469f29af56529d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F145717_4d5b00cb8685042b20469f29af56529d.jpg&h=82145e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nbefore<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/143414_77bebc05ed395ae81f084b01c82c68e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F143414_77bebc05ed395ae81f084b01c82c68e5.jpg&h=a69359db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次smoke blue 預期結果會係偏灰嘅藍<br />\n<br />\n其實我有上網揾過下d實測睇 不過好多人無漂過就用 所以好難知實際個效果點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/143737_6970e1208d694eb1a03745244ff7e546.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F143737_6970e1208d694eb1a03745244ff7e546.jpg&h=b4a5b281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n擠出嚟係咁<br />\n<br />\n染完後...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/144004_ec37cbf68eddf4184d33962d192f077c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F144004_ec37cbf68eddf4184d33962d192f077c.jpg&h=ff2fcbec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n布甸頭 大家可以睇到漂過同未漂過嘅頭用呢包野出嘅色嘅分別<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/144145_d19f87c582daeae5f22fbb2365dc553e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F144145_d19f87c582daeae5f22fbb2365dc553e.jpg&h=f25142e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑色頭髮染完就啡 金果d就灰灰地藍藍地咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/144436_054f5fdc2d9c6d81751136636f58594f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F144436_054f5fdc2d9c6d81751136636f58594f.jpg&h=f41a5021&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇真d!其實係又啡又金又少少灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢張有d恐怖反映左我個頭嘅柒況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能我查得唔勻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n得閒無野做所以開呢個po分享下 比起上次個紅色 呢隻色明顯安全得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過下次都係出去染算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇左少少片之後我覺得如果巴絲想試呢包野但無漂過頭應該得紅色出到少少色 其他色就應該都係晒錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw呢隻色去影見工相得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a9b763b628707277ab95ec58cd5e7bb636f924","tid":365340,"uid":137977,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T07:00:45.000Z","msg":"認真有少少柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68715e04b767d1a741473c2ff878690cae89bce","tid":365340,"uid":79981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真有少少柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺唔靚 不過係出得街嘅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90109379b9b9b7429fff8fd84ce23a8e032cf8f","tid":365340,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"幾好呀<img src=\"